Package org.junit.runners.parameterized

Interface Summary
ParametersRunnerFactory A ParameterizedRunnerFactory creates a runner for a single TestWithParameters.
 

Class Summary
BlockJUnit4ClassRunnerWithParameters A BlockJUnit4ClassRunner with parameters support.
BlockJUnit4ClassRunnerWithParametersFactory A ParametersRunnerFactory that creates BlockJUnit4ClassRunnerWithParameters.
TestWithParameters A TestWithParameters keeps the data together that are needed for creating a runner for a single data set of a parameterized test.
